data.description: Well maintained home in the Tyler Ridge Subdivision with over 3500sqft of living space. Home boasts 2 story Foyer entrance, 5 bedroom, 3 1/2 bath, along with 3 living areas. Features large Island with Granite Tops throughout, stainless appliances w/double oven and hardwood flooring throughout Kitchen, Formal dining, living room and Family room. Tile in wet areas and carpet in the bedrooms and fresh paint throughout. Exterior features covered front porch and rear covered patio. Large lot with sod, irrigation and professional landscaping.
